{"tid":1683335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我思疑呢班人干犯非法集結+蒙面法，可以點做？","createTime":"2019-10-30T15:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T12:18:14.000Z","uid":230104,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8addf5a959bce9201932631dc61124acdba63964","tid":1683335,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:03:11.000Z","msg":"【何謂非法集結？何以執行公安條例？】<br />\n<br />\n公安條例第18條寫明，「凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作出擾亂秩序的行為或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，他們即屬非法集結。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CGmGPWG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCGmGPWG.png&h=10f4f996&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iS04NJY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiS04NJY.png&h=b3d4cfed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"244837c528ad5c98b55927b0646ad4af3ff82f58","tid":1683335,"uid":36158,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"唔好再對法律有幻想啦<br />\n仲係到懶醒想用法律去煮返死對家<br />\n係得既就唔會淪落到而家咁啦<br />\n醒啦"},{"pid":"82d9cc9fa6ac21ccc29d7cb72abf0f3708d410e3","tid":1683335,"uid":70897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"冇用都要做，照督灰等佢地變condom。唔好比籍口佢地話冇人報警之類。所有低成本嘅嘢都要做，做個良好市民嘛"},{"pid":"d7cd90739841e5852606b066abc04254826044db","tid":1683335,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"要揭露多D佢地幾執法不公、選擇性執法既案例<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/naV4NMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnaV4NMU.png&h=459d8c27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68ba37b61d47953611909476aed09f7413d6466a","tid":1683335,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4981be2f2da9e0611ec572e73fc7bc1e29d1d23","tid":1683335,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:19:59